description: Try our easy to follow Lamingtons recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Lamington,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Low salt,Tree nut free,Sesame free,Quick & easy dessert,Peanut free
name: Lamingtons Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Trim edges of 1 sponge cake layer. Cut into 12 cubes measuring 5cm each. Place onto a baking tray lined with baking paper and freeze for 30 minutes.

Meanwhile, sift icing sugar and cocoa together into a heatproof bowl. Place bowl over a saucepan of simmering water. Add melted butter and milk, stirring until smooth and glossy. Place coconut into a separate large bowl.
Using two forks, dip each cake square into the icing to completely coat, then toss in coconut. Place onto a wire rack over a tray. Leave until set.
